<view class='shade' hidden='{{popup}}' bindtap='hidePopup'></view>
<view class='shade_box popup' hidden='{{popup}}'>
    <view class='title'><text>认证成功</text></view>
    <view class='content'> 恭喜您认证成功，获得1.2倍里程加速！</view>
    <button type="primary" open-type="share" class="btn">分享给好友</button>
    <view class='copy'>好友通过你的分享进入汽车人生，你将额外获得300里程奖励！</view>
    <view class='msg' bindtap='hidePopup'>
      <image src="../../images/close.png"></image>
    </view>
</view>
<view  style='margin:20rpx 50rpx;'>
    <button type='primary' bindtap='showPopup'>打开弹窗</button>
</view>
